,"reblog-key":"HZMmYXHk","slug":"allstar-washingtonnationals-glove-save-and-a","photo-caption":"<p>#AllStar<\/p>\n<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"http:\/\/washingtonnationals.tumblr.com\/post\/87406741350\/glove-save-and-a-beauty-what-a-slick-play-by\">washingtonnationals<\/a>:<\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Glove save and a beauty! What a slick play by Anthony Rendon.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>","width":"400","height":"225","photo-url-1280":"http:\/\/33.media.tumblr.com\/d6d4e5737f2b828b4224d33afd671968\/tumblr_n6g7ouM4ep1rs13mso1_400.gif","photo-url-500":"http:\/\/33.media.tumblr.com\/d6d4e5737f2b828b4224d33afd671968\/tumblr_n6g7ouM4ep1rs13mso1_400.gif","photo-url-400":"http:\/\/33.media.tumblr.com\/d6d4e5737f2b828b4224d33afd671968\/tumblr_n6g7ouM4ep1rs13mso1_400.gif","photo-url-250":"http:\/\/38.media.tumblr.com\/d6d4e5737f2b828b4224d33afd671968\/tumblr_n6g7ouM4ep1rs13mso1_250.gif","photo-url-100":"http:\/\/38.media.tumblr.com\/d6d4e5737f2b828b4224d33afd671968\/tumblr_n6g7ouM4ep1rs13mso1_100.gif","photo-url-75":"http:\/\/33.media.tumblr.com\/d6d4e5737f2b828b4224d33afd671968\/tumblr_n6g7ouM4ep1rs13mso1_75sq.gif","photos":[]},{"id":"89267951369","url":"http:\/\/pitchersandpoets.tumblr.com\/post\/89267951369","url-with-slug":"http:\/\/pitchersandpoets.tumblr.com\/post\/89267951369\/claytonia","type":"regular","date-gmt":"2014-06-19 16:00:53 GMT","date":"Thu, 19 Jun 2014 09:00:53","bookmarklet":0,"mobile":0,"feed-item":"","from-feed-id":0,"unix-timestamp":1403193653,"format":"html","reblog-key":"SNBiKCEl","slug":"claytonia","regular-title":"Claytonia","regular-body":"<p><span>It\u2019s amazing what a peaceful Wednesday evening can bring in baseball land.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span>I fired up what I thought would be some meaningless West Coast baseball.\u00a0<\/span>What I found was a bit more&#8230;animated.<\/p>\n<p><span>Dodgers-Rockies. Charlie Steiner, the LA radio man, went on about Uncle Charlie, Clayton Kershaw\u2019s legendary curveball. \u201cWhen I say Uncle Charlie, I mean a curveball that can freeze you right up\u2026\u201d etc. Baseball 101.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span>Twitter informed me that he was doing his superstitious best to avoid any mention of the feat unfolding before him. Steiner and his broadcasting partner instead praised the characteristics of public enemy number one, the curveball that launched a thousand strikeouts.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span>They dodged the words \u201cno\u201d and \u201chitter\u201d like they might summon a baseball demon; the fear of the baseball gods were in them.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span>Dodgers.com was kind enough to make their streaming video available to those of us too cheap to pay for the privilege. I felt bad switching from radio to TV and abandoning Charlie &amp; Friends at the pivotal moment.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span>Vin Scully quickly alleviated my guilt.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span>\u201cIf you don\u2019t mind, I\u2019m just gonna sit back and watch with the rest of you,\u201d said Vin. A legend in the booth watching a hero on the field. Twitter buzzed with Vinsanity as much as Kershawesomeness.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span>The ace struck out the last batter, he raised both arms. He really takes up some space, especially when unfolded. Michaelangelo would need half a mountain\u2019s worth of marble.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b1941c43-b4d9-dd3a-ae3a-e02113441451\"><span>- Ted<\/span><\/span><\/p>","tags":["clayton kershaw","dodgers","Vin Scully"]},{"id":"88978646939","url":"http:\/\/pitchersandpoets.tumblr.com\/post\/88978646939","url-with-slug":"http:\/\/pitchersandpoets.tumblr.com\/post\/88978646939\/the-humility-of-tony-gwynn-vice-sports","type":"link","date-gmt":"2014-06-16 18:54:39 GMT","date":"Mon, 16 Jun 2014 11:54:39","bookmarklet":0,"mobile":0,"feed-item":"","from-feed-id":0,"unix-timestamp":1402944879,"format":"html","reblog-key":"z7TI0Amu","slug":"the-humility-of-tony-gwynn-vice-sports","link-text":"The Humility of Tony Gwynn | VICE Sports","link-url":"https:\/\/sports.vice.com\/article\/the-humility-of-tony-gwynn","link-description":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"http:\/\/ericnus.com\/post\/88974436012\/the-humility-of-tony-gwynn-vice-sports\">ericnus<\/a>:<\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"link_og_blockquote\">\n<div>Remembering Tony Gwynn for all that he was to San Diego and baseball.<\/div>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>I wrote a little bit about the wonderful Tony Gwynn for Vice Sports.\u00a0<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>"},{"id":"88618989079","url":"http:\/\/pitchersandpoets.tumblr.com\/post\/88618989079","url-with-slug":"http:\/\/pitchersandpoets.tumblr.com\/post\/88618989079\/someone-please-tell-me-what-this-is-and-why-this","type":"photo","date-gmt":"2014-06-13 00:26:01 GMT","date":"Thu, 12 Jun 2014 17:26:01","bookmarklet":0,"mobile":0,"feed-item":"","from-feed-id":0,"unix-timestamp":1402619161,"format":"html","reblog-key":"vYDValB8","slug":"someone-please-tell-me-what-this-is-and-why-this","photo-caption":"<p>someone please tell me what this is and why this is<\/p>","width":"1218","height":"1222","photo-url-1280":"http:\/\/38.media.tumblr.com\/04cd5f327e860b588b481a9a62a11e2c\/tumblr_n72vhkC20M1skwocko1_1280.png","photo-url-500":"http:\/\/38.media.tumblr.com\/04cd5f327e860b588b481a9a62a11e2c\/tumblr_n72vhkC20M1skwocko1_500.png","photo-url-400":"http:\/\/31.media.tumblr.com\/04cd5f327e860b588b481a9a62a11e2c\/tumblr_n72vhkC20M1skwocko1_400.png","photo-url-250":"http:\/\/38.media.tumblr.com\/04cd5f327e860b588b481a9a62a11e2c\/tumblr_n72vhkC20M1skwocko1_250.png","photo-url-100":"http:\/\/31.media.tumblr.com\/04cd5f327e860b588b481a9a62a11e2c\/tumblr_n72vhkC20M1skwocko1_100.png","photo-url-75":"http:\/\/31.media.tumblr.com\/04cd5f327e860b588b481a9a62a11e2c\/tumblr_n72vhkC20M1skwocko1_75sq.png","photos":[]},{"id":"87705026844","url":"http:\/\/pitchersandpoets.tumblr.com\/post\/87705026844","url-with-slug":"http:\/\/pitchersandpoets.tumblr.com\/post\/87705026844\/sandwich-baseball-gif-of-the-year","type":"photo","date-gmt":"2014-06-03 16